## AI Agent Instructions
- **Context Awareness:** When drafting features, always prioritize the "3-Role" model: **Issuer** (HR), **Holder** (Candidate), and **Verifier** (Recruiter).
- **Privacy First:** All data-related code must respect the DPDP Act principles outlined in the Compliance Nightmare section.
- **Zero-Knowledge Preference:** Favor proofs over data transfers whenever a verification requirement can be met without revealing PII.